{"tid":1628671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[我要分化] 如果我係政府, 我會咁做","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:55:20.000Z","uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"24719f8c6547b3653be486903713a7d42623d492","tid":1628671,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:08:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">[我係FF 撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />]</span><br />\n<ins><strong>港島區</strong></ins><br />\n今日全部和理非入晒港島<br />\n港島順利完成遊行, 乜事都無, 乜狗都無<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>九龍區</strong></ins><br />\n九龍區勇武集中<br />\n搵幾個UC 亂扑亂燒舖<br />\n三中商又亂咁燒, 連9唔搭8 既中資都攪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二日, 政府希望和理非同勇武割蓆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割你老母呀割!</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地呢埸運動最大優勢係<br />\n不分化, 不篤灰, 不割蓆!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋輸左呢場仗<br />\n我地係無得翻身架! 生生世世為中共奴隸!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">勇武前線衝衝子</span>, 佢地都係受過<span style=\"color: red;\">高等教育既香港人</span>黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地全香港人都<span style=\"color: blue;\">相信佢地</span>可以<span style=\"color: red;\">明白大局</span>, <span style=\"color: orange;\">明白有乜可以做, 有乜唔可以做</span><br />\n我地唔係暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地係以武制暴既香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">相信勇武<br />\n和理不分</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩點見!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a56e303a678d4ce42d0360a328e9abc60696437","tid":1628671,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:11:24.000Z","msg":"推多幾下等陣見!"},{"pid":"230015e1cd0e1ea62f8b159d9c82878ce8808d36","tid":1628671,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"推多幾下等陣見!"},{"pid":"700671c93f88a78598485d61dc3df413be020004","tid":1628671,"uid":91017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"我留意過幾次, 根本前線好多有勇冇謀<br />\n1. 買通渠佬做魔法, 有飛魚, 哥士唔去買<br />\n2. 填左白膠漿既磚唔去撬, le d其實大一字批加鎚仔或重物扑就nut<br />\n<br />\n重有好多問题..........."},{"pid":"296be6b59248397f1438d535ee9938ec73d4d9e0","tid":1628671,"uid":264988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:55:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}